claim.claim-text:
A vehicle (100) comprising:
a frame (101) comprising a first fixing point (110) and a second fixing point (111);
a drive shaft (107) fixed to the frame (101);
an actuating element (109) pivotably fixed to the frame (101) at the first fixing point (110) and moveable by a stroke along a movement path;
a driving element (112) fixed to the frame (101) at the second fixing point (111) and coupled to the drive shaft (107); and
a deflection element (220) coupled to the actuating element (109),

wherein the drive shaft (107) is arranged between the first fixing point (110) and the second fixing point (111); and

wherein the deflection element (220) is coupled to the actuating element (109) in such a way that during a stroke the deflection element (220) deflects the driving element (112).
